# Auto-peel dwell keyframe A (see l1000-autopeel.mac).
# Paired with b.g4view; the two are 0.5 deg apart so /vis/viewer/interpolate
# always animates (never short-circuits) and thus always honours wait-time.
# Matches l1000-vis.mac's default viewpoint (70 20).
/vis/viewer/set/viewpointThetaPhi 70 20 deg
/vis/viewer/set/lightsThetaPhi 70 20 deg
